"gehören der Fuloong Mini-PC und der Lemote Yeeloong Laptop."

#. Tag: term
#: hardware.xml:907
#, no-c-format
msgid "SGI IP22"
msgstr "SGI IP22"

#. Tag: listitem
#: hardware.xml:908
#, no-c-format
msgid "This platform includes the SGI machines Indy, Indigo 2 and Challenge S."
msgstr ""
